      • downloadAttachment

        ClipboardPage downloadAttachment(java.lang.String aInstanceHandle,
                                 java.lang.String aAttachmentHandle)
        download attachment content from a secondary storage by its handle. As part of this call actual attachment files for internal attachments is downloaded in browser. In case of correspondence attachment instance is returned.Additional APIs should be called to display it.
        Parameters:
        aInstanceHandle - the handle of its parent instance
        aAttachmentHandle - the handle of attachment instance to download
        Returns:
        the requested attachment instance
